title: Hour 2 - Mike Vrabel (05-13-20)
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Mike Vrabel (05-13-20)
description:
Tennessee Titan Head Coach Mike Vrabel talks about all the touchdown passes he caught from Tom Brady. Mike tells Dan about the time he made the mistake of coming back to the huddle to tell Brady that he was wide open.
